comment:
Phoolan Devi is a conflicting , and multi- layered personality : she was beaten , sexually assaulted , wed to a much older man , defiled and made a second - class citizen in her own state and wronged by people belonging to the law enforcement agency(cops ) , and therefore it is understandable she went down the path of bloodshed and crime. .

But , we also have to recognise that mulayam singh yadav ( the supremo of samajwadi party ) had a instrumental role to play in her release and telecast of her surrender : he made the capture of a nefarious criminal into a national circus , and pardoned her despite the severity of her crime ( roberry , arson and kidnapping ) , and she became a symbol of lower class resistence and mythical heroine for lower castes , in an era of upper - caste ( savarna domination ) , but largely media had a bigger role to play in heroicizing and garlanding her as a independent and honorific lady.
